name: Midnight Putlocker
description: Designed to be easier on the eyes, this theme is simple and clean. Recommended for anyone who enjoys using Putlocker.
additional_info: Recommended extensions (Chrome) • AdBlock, blocks the ads on Putlocker and ads everywhere else on the web • Putlocker Next Episode, adds a 'next episode' button to the show you're watching Recent Updates April 26, 2017 • Now works on the even newer URL (putlocker.co) November 14th • Now works on the new URL • Changed the theme name • Other minor tweaks September 26th • Cleaned up Nav bar • Font touch ups September 19th • New "Play Video" buttons July 4th • Small clean up July 3rd • Cleaned up the custom logo • Cleaned up the Search bar • Fixed small errors June 21st • Recreated home Search button + other small clean ups June 20th • New Scrollbar • Cleaned up the Home Page   • Recoloured and resized the text input boxes and dropdown menus   • Removed unnecessary cluttering links • Recoloured Search bar • Resized fonts
